[quote=“Coder X, post:7, topic:173826”][quote author=Songoty link=topic=234160.msg1999898#msg1999898 date=1200512837]

Does anyone know of a server that laggs less then others. I know for a fact PkWarIsle laggs less then others and it’s huge, but i don’t feel like working with it.

You Know, its not just server sources themselves that lag, its your internet and what else that you are doing that inflicts it to.
Get a blank source, theres nothing there, so it should reduce your lag a bit.
[/quote]

-.- i know…and it has nothing to do with your internet.[/quote]
Oh, i see, so running a server does not inflict your bandwith?
If your on the internet downloading a file, the server is going to lag, because it has to share the connection with something else.
